    "generatedAt": "2026-04-25",
    "notes": [
      "All ObjectId values are transported as 24-char hex string.",
      "Date-time values use ISO-8601 UTC string.",
      "This contract is aligned to current backend code.",
      "For FormField tipo=file, frontend sends multipart/form-data in process_complete_activity, including files and field mapping in same request."
